{"tid":2125252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賓客串連稻香富臨群組  至少58確診 疑有人瞞報行蹤","createTime":"2020-07-26T05:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T13:50:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":276,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd750194e4033fe4ac11d63dd3cc1019b5d72e8","tid":2125252,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:21:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/K3DROGMLSIQZVC4JXMOEWD4ZE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FK3DROGMLSIQZVC4JXMOEWD4ZE4%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLnvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=d0e3d372\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FK3DROGMLSIQZVC4JXMOEWD4ZE4%2F&h=8f5e225f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/K3DROGMLSIQZVC4JXMOEWD4ZE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n賓客串連稻香富臨群組 <br />\n至少58確診 疑有人瞞報行蹤<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UFuQwKFLECWjmFYxr_4BImVChEk=/709x492/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WWQ4CWG4MKVWFHOBTLNCZEJ3BA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUFuQwKFLECWjmFYxr_4BImVChEk%3D%2F709x492%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWWQ4CWG4MKVWFHOBTLNCZEJ3BA.gif&h=99cadcb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣悅來坊肯德基有一名員工確診，分店昨已關閉，並在門外貼出告示通知顧客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】載歌載舞的旺角稻香慶回歸晚宴群組再多4人確診，令群組人數增至33人；屯門富臨群組亦多5人確診，群組人數增至25人。衞生防護中心調查發現，幾個宴會群組其實有關連，可能是有隱形患者出席了多個宴會傳播病毒。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨公佈，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部份人再涉德記群組<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鄧達智感染 曾與徐小鳳飯敍<br />\n<br />\n7月11日屯門中央廣場。。。。。。。。。。。。。整個屯門富臨群組至今累計25宗個案。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君指出，調查發現部份確診患者曾去過稻香及富臨兩個宴會，包括宴會上的表演者，之後又有人去過有兩名食客確診的西環德記潮州菜館宴會，部份人又涉及不同家庭群組及其他多個小型宴會。各宴會群組之間其實互相有關連，「呢啲大聚會，如果有啲隱性患者喺到，大家好開心咁唱歌，容易引起傳播。」<br />\n<br />\n屯門富臨壽宴有約200人參與，衞生防護中心一直無交代是否已全部成功追蹤。屯門民主派區議員聯名去信衞生署長，指屯門富臨壽宴群組無視疫情及法例，導致社區爆發，更已出現數代傳播。近日有街坊透露，<span class=\"orange\">有壽宴參加者因擔心法律後果而拒絕透露行蹤，以致當局追查困難</span>。區議會要求當局命令壽宴主辦人向衞生署交出參加者名單，全部安排隔離檢疫，以堵塞防疫漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n必勝客 肯德基員工中招<br />\n<br />\n張竹君又指出，確診歌手麥德羅曾表演的尖沙嘴Superstar Live Music 酒廊有一名職員確診。酒廊之前已有一名顧客確診。灣仔雅園餐廳小廚亦有一名員工確診。而近日亦有個別外賣速遞員確診個案，但數目不多。<br />\n<br />\n必勝客昨在facebook公佈，薄扶林置富分店一名兼職外送速遞員確診，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n肯德基荃灣悅來坊分店亦有一名兼職員工確診，肯。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d66464593920e905951d94741cdb7abbe6115fe4","tid":2125252,"uid":132587,"like":260,"dislike":3,"score":257,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7f6e7bf7ffb8fc072b5ffcb3563b20465755a7b","tid":2125252,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a55af714b0b790c8efa0d46e9d1d43de9b6b61","tid":2125252,"uid":44160,"like":76,"dislike":2,"score":74,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"去過叫雞，搵二奶，又話你知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe6e0a884bdb58bcc8fd218f295321229ad3179","tid":2125252,"uid":77196,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"藍屍死多幾件最好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e919ab5a63fb1be608e8e7beb79bdf22cfe9d0","tid":2125252,"uid":245388,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"做得好最好不斷傳染翻比自己藍絲群"},{"pid":"8032ab2ae7826788f2ddfc13619e2839685